text: "Rang Brown Ni" is a Punjabi language song sung by Kaptan Laadi. Upon the release the song get captured positive reviews both from the critics and the audience. The video was released on 9 July 2019. it was the Going to the biggest hit of the following year. It has Feature the most popular dancer in India Sapna Choudhary ==References== Category:2019 songs Category:Punjabi- language songs
title: Rang Brown Ni
